title: Introduction to the Human Body - Anatomy and Physiology
description:
Introduction to the Human Body: The Essentials of Anatomy and Physiology
By Gerard J. Tortora and Bryan H. Derrickson 
Wiley; 9 edition (May 1, 2012)
748 pages
PDF


This book offers a balanced introduction to the human body especially developed to meet the needs of the one semester course. It provides an effective blend of stunning art and clearly written text to illuminate the complexities of the human body. Class-tested pedagogy is woven into the narrative and figures to ensure that students gain a solid understanding of the material
